# Browser Extension Overview

This project is a browser extension with the following key files:

*   **[manifest.json](mdc:manifest.json)**: The manifest file that defines the extension's properties and permissions.
*   **[background/background.js](mdc:background/background.js)**: Handles background tasks and events.
*   **[content_scripts/content.js](mdc:content_scripts/content.js)**: A general content script injected into web pages.
*   **[ui/popup/popup.html](mdc:ui/popup/popup.html)** and **[ui/popup/popup.js](mdc:ui/popup/popup.js)**: Define the extension's popup UI and its logic.
*   **[ui/options/options.html](mdc:ui/options/options.html)** and **[ui/options/options.js](mdc:ui/options/options.js)**: Define the extension's options page UI and its logic.

It also includes content scripts for specific websites located in the `content_scripts/` directory:

*   **[content_scripts/ai_studio_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/ai_studio_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/chatgpt_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/chatgpt_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/claude_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/claude_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/gemini_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/gemini_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/grok_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/grok_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/perplexity_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/perplexity_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/youtube_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/youtube_content.js)**
*   **[content_scripts/reddit_content.js](mdc:content_scripts/reddit_content.js)**

Other important files include:

*   **[ui/options/options.css](mdc:ui/options/options.css)**: Provides styling for the options page.
*   **images/**: Contains images used by the extension.